headline: HCA Healthcare Commits $150,000 in Support of Veterans and Their Families in Honor of Veterans Day
summary: NASHVILLE, Tenn., November 11, 2025--HCA Healthcare, Inc. (NYSE:HCA), one of the nation’s leading healthcare providers, today announced it will give $150,000 to multiple veteran support organizations in honor of Veterans Day. Since 2012, HCA Healthcare has hired more than 65,000 veterans, active-duty and reserve personnel and military spouses.
